WEBVTT

00:00:01.122 --> 00:00:02.813
Afo gara-aga...

00:00:02.837 --> 00:00:04.040
dirim ka oku.

00:00:04.064 --> 00:00:05.861
(Ichi ochi)

00:00:05.871 --> 00:00:11.113
O bukwa oge mbu,
m riri osikapa "joloofu" ndi Naijiria.

00:00:11.227 --> 00:00:12.759
(Ichi ochi)

00:00:13.786 --> 00:00:17.475
N' eziokwu, 


00:00:17.499 --> 00:00:20.313
ihe m gabigara buru ibu.

00:00:20.785 --> 00:00:23.416
N' etiti nnukwu nsogbu m,

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:25.463
A gabigakwala m nnukwu egwu.

00:00:26.542 --> 00:00:29.232
Ufodu Ubochi,
E nweghim ike iru aru oru.